## Three.js VR
```javascript
import { VRButton } from 'three/addons/webxr/VRButton.js';
renderer.xr.enabled = true;
document.body.appendChild(VRButton.createButton(renderer));
const controller = renderer.xr.getController(0);
controller.addEventListener('selectstart', onSelectStart);
scene.add(controller);
// Render loop
renderer.setAnimationLoop(() => renderer.render(scene, camera));
```

## Single Pass Stereo
Unity:
```csharp
// PlayerSettings → XR → Stereo Rendering Mode:
// Single Pass Instanced seç
// Shader'lar UNITY_STEREO_INSTANCING_ENABLED ile güncellenmeli
```
Unreal: Project Settings → VR → Instanced Stereo = true.
Fayda: GPU draw call sayısı yarıya düşer.

## Quest Passthrough
```csharp
using UnityEngine.XR.Management;
// OVRManager ekle
OVRManager.instance.isInsightPassthroughEnabled = true;
var passthroughLayer = GetComponent<OVRPassthroughLayer>();
passthroughLayer.overlayType = OVROverlay.OverlayType.Underlay;
// Skybox'ı şeffaf yap: clear flags = Solid Color, alpha = 0
```

## Spatial Audio
Unity: AudioSource → Spatial Blend = 1 (3D).
Plugin: Resonance Audio veya Steam Audio (binaural HRTF).
```csharp
AudioSource src = GetComponent<AudioSource>();
src.spatialBlend = 1.0f;
src.rolloffMode = AudioRolloffMode.Logarithmic;
src.maxDistance = 20f;
// Steam Audio Spatializer: Inspector'dan seç
```
